Slice pork tenderloin in half lengthwise; then slice crosswise into 1/4-inch thick slices. Melt 2 Saute Express(R) squares in 12-inch nonstick skillet over medium-low heat just until bubbles begin to form. Add pork. Saute 4-5 minutes or until pork is done. Remove from skillet. Melt remaining 1 Saute Express(R) square in skillet. Add stir-fry vegetables, onion and water chestnuts. Cook 4 to 5 minutes or until tender; stir in pork.